      "rationale": "Testing was conducted at a single ASTM F1717 configuration (44 mm vertebral body spacer, 10 mm pedicle offset). Only one test condition was evaluated, which is below the required level 2. This factor is identified as a gap; the overall credibility assessment remains Accepted because all other factors meet or exceed required levels and the validation uncertainty metric E/uval <1.96 is satisfied."
